cts the repository virtual environment before running rebar, make lint, make typecheck, or other development gates.\n- Provision the current isolated worktree using the documented workflow and verify both gates without changing their implementation or formatting unrelated files.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] AGENTS.md tells Codex sessions how to bootstrap and activate the repository environment using the same documented workflow as Claude Code.\n- [ ] The guidance prevents ambient Ruff or missing mypy from being mistaken for repository failures.\n- [ ] make lint exits zero in the correctly configured worktree.\n- [ ] make typecheck exits zero in the correctly configured worktree.\n- [ ] The change cites the authoritative project setup documentation and remains concise.\n","env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","file_impact":[{"path":"AGENTS.md","reason":"Persist Codex worktree virtualenv setup for reproducible development gates"}],"keyring":[],"last_status_env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","managed_refs":[],"parent_id":null,"parent_status_uuid":"15713361-b6b1-4caf-b2dd-ea1826528089","preconditions_summary":{"status":"pre-manifest"},"priority":2,"reverts":[],"status":"in_progress","tags":[],"ticket_id":"99c7-3f0e-3685-484f","ticket_type":"task","title":"Document Codex repository environment setup","verify_commands":[]},"source_event_uuids":["c9a5fc58-89d4-4ff2-a2a9-064a19bbd18a","7deb37e9-c3c8-48c5-ad94-0a5d07d3e240","b337a135-303e-4022-b9eb-bbf066681106","15713361-b6b1-4caf-b2dd-ea1826528089","65f9347e-ded5-4063-b2ad-37fb5e106194","0c9c8493-b9ad-4e7a-906c-8a5dc03a0a3f","a821c5b7-9b46-47f3-b408-f466abfb90c1"]},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"SNAPSHOT","timestamp":1784656472713252957,"uuid":"cfdebae6-7426-40e4-83b3-d183065b08df"}